info.author: Michael Schilonka
info.description: # Getdeck Beiboot _Getdeck Beiboot_ (or just Beiboot for brevity) is a Kubernetes-in-Kubernetes solution. It was born from the idea to provide Getdeck users a simple yet flexible solution to spin up **hybrid cloud development** infrastructure. This is useful for Kubernetes development workloads which grew too large to run on a development machine (or with pony workloads on MacOS and Windows machines). # Beiboot Client The Beiboot client is a Python API to manage Beiboot clusters. It can set up and tear down Kubernetes instances as well as establish connections.
